# Tag roots to migrate from AEM → Sanity.
#
# `aem-tags` walks every namespace (or subtree) listed here and emits one
# Sanity `category` document per AEM `cq:Tag` node. Authored content's
# `cq:tags` references are then rewritten to Sanity reference arrays
# pointing at those categories during `aem-transform`.
#
# Only what's listed below is migrated. There's no canonical "always skip"
# set in AEM — sample-content namespaces like `wknd` or `we-retail` are
# simply absent from this file. Add them if you want them.
#
# Syntax mirrors aem-content-roots:
#   @base /content/cq:tags    → optional base for relative entries below
#   promotion                 → relative to the current @base
#   /content/cq:tags/wknd     → absolute (overrides @base)
#
# Tip: hit `<AEM_AUTHOR_URL>/content/cq:tags.1.json` while logged into AEM
# author to list every namespace under your tag root.

